# textdomain: mcl_signs
Sign=告示牌
Can be written=可以写字
Signs can be written and come in two variants: Wall sign and sign on a sign post. Signs can be placed on the top and the sides of other blocks, but not below them.=告示牌可以书写内容，并有两种变体：墙上告示牌和立在告示牌柱上的告示牌。告示牌可放置在其他方块的顶部和侧面，但不能放置在它们的下方。
After placing the sign, you can write something on it. You have 4 lines of text with up to 15 characters for each line; anything beyond these limits is lost. Not all characters are supported. The text can not be changed once it has been written; you have to break and place the sign again. Can be colored and made to glow.=放置好告示牌后，你可以在上面书写内容。你有四行文本空间，每行最多可写15个字符，超出这些限制的内容将会丢失。并非所有字符都能被支持。文字一旦写好就无法更改，你必须破坏告示牌然后重新放置才能修改内容。告示牌可以被染色并设置为发光状态。
Enter sign text:=输入文字：
Maximum line length: 15=每行限制：15
Maximum lines: 4=行数限制：4
Done=完成
